N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 5 ยง 101.1 - Members

State Regulations

The members of the board shall be the Commissioner of

Commerce, the Commissioner of Taxation and Finance, the Commissioner of Labor, the Commissioner of Agriculture and Markets, the Secretary of State, the

Commissioner of Housing and Community Renewal, the chairman of the State Board
of Equalization and Assessment, and such other State officer as the Governor
shall designate, all serving ex officio and without salary. Notes
